These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, green, black, blue
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, house, funk
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the person who likes black##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
5. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Color   | brown | green | blue | black |
| Music-Genre        | blues | dubstep   | funk | house    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, sprite, tea
House: cape-cod, craftsman, modern, cottage
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the modern house is in an odd position##4
4. the cape-cod house is the person drinking milk##1
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the modern house##1
6. the cape-cod house is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk  | soy-milk  | tea |
| House   | cottage    | cape-cod | modern | craftsman    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, cola, sprite
House: tower, victorian, townhouse, futuristic
1. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3
2. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
3. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
4. the futuristic house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
5. the tower house is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage          | sprite | cola | milk    | mirinda      |
| House   | townhouse        | futuristic     | tower | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, mystery, epic, satire
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, july, june
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in june##2
2. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | satire | superhero | mystery | epic |
| Birthday   | july       | january   | march    | june  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, electrician, dressmaker, dancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, van, snowmobile, boat
1. the dressmaker is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person driving the van is the dancer##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the electrician is on the far left##1
5. the dressmaker is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Job   | electrician  | fisherman    | dressmaker   | dancer       |
| Transport   | airplane | boat | snowmobile | van |

