.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, magic-tricks, baking
City: hamburg, colone, prague, paris
1. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks      | rock-climbing | baking | skydiving |
| City   | paris | colone     | hamburg  | prague  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
House: modern, tower, art-deco, townhouse
4 different pets are kept: fish, lizard, turtle, rat
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the owner of the rat is the modern house##1
5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| House   | modern | townhouse | art-deco | tower    |
| Pet     | rat | turtle  | fish     | lizard |

