.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold, begonia, bellflower
House: cottage, modern, craftsman, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
2. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
3. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person who growsbellflower##3
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the townhouse house##1
5. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsmarigold##2
6. the modern house is in an odd position##4
7. the modern house is between the person who growstulip and the craftsman house##2
8. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Flower   | marigold | tulip      | bellflower | begonia |
| House   | cottage  | townhouse | modern    | craftsman            |

