.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
House: cottage, art-deco, ranch-style, victorian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, d&b, metal, house
1. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
2. the cottage house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
3. the fan of pop is between the fan of d&b and the ranch-style house##2
4. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
5. the ranch-style house is the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| House   | victorian | art-deco   | cottage | ranch-style |
| Music-Genre    | house     | d&b | pop     | metal  |

