.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, skateboarding, snowboarding, tennis
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, december, february
1. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
4. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Sport      | skateboarding       | snowboarding   | rugby | tennis |
| Birthday   | december | june | february        | october    |

