.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
City: hannover, boston, rome, london
4 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, goldfish, london-polo
1. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the london-polo##1
4. the owner of the london-polo is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| City   | hannover   | london   | boston      | rome      |
| Pet      | guinea-pig | goldfish | london-polo | snake |

