.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different games are played: domino, billiard, whist, canasta
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, card-games, gardening, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Game   | whist | canasta | domino | billiard |
| Hobby           | drawing     | rock-climbing     | gardening   | card-games         |

