.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, nurse, pilot, teacher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, techno, classical, folk
1. the electrician is between the fan of ambient and the nurse##2
2. the pilot is on the far left or far right##3
3. the nurse is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the nurse##1
5. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Job   | teacher | nurse         | electrician   | pilot |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | techno | folk | ambient   |

