.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, backgammon, chess
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, electronic, d&b, country
1. the fan of country is the person playing backgammon##1
2. the fan of d&b is the person playing poker##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
5. the person playing poker is in an even position##4
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg | poker | backgammon    | chess |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | d&b  | country | electronic     |

