.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, motorbike, helicopter, subway
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, white, light-blue, green
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes white is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
5. the person who likes white is between the person who likes green and the person who likes light-blue##2
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport         | subway   | helicopter | roller | motorbike    |
| Color   | light-blue | white  | green     | chestnut |

