.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
City: london, san-francisco, berlin, paris
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, vegafina, chaman, dunhill
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
3. the person traveling to paris is on the far left or far right##3
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
6. the chaman-smoker is in an even position##4
7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| City   | paris | london    | berlin       | san-francisco |
| Cigar       | vegafina  | chaman | dunhill | ritmeester  |

