.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, turquise, amber, ivory
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, sailing, handball, rowing
1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color   | turquise | amber | brown  | ivory |
| Sport     | golf      | handball       | sailing | rowing     |

