.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, mah-jongg, bridge
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, alhambra, cain, bluemaster
1. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
3. the alhambra-smoker is between the person playing monopoly and the aristoff-smoker##2
4. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3
5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
6. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Game         | monopoly | mah-jongg   | bridge | scrabble |
| Cigar   | bluemaster          | alhambra | aristoff         | cain  |

 